表的代码预览通知

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('tell') and o.name = 'FK_TELL_TELL_COLLECTO')
alter table tell
drop constraint FK_TELL_TELL_COLLECTO
go

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('tell') and o.name = 'FK_TELL_TELL2_PATIENT')
alter table tell
drop constraint FK_TELL_TELL2_PATIENT
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('tell')
and name = 'tell_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index tell.tell_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('tell')
and name = 'tell2_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index tell.tell2_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('tell')
and type = 'U')
drop table tell
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: tell */
/*==============================================================*/
create table tell (
cno char(8) not null,
pno char(8) not null,
constraint PK_TELL primary key nonclustered (cno, pno)
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: tell2_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index tell2_FK on tell (
pno ASC
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: tell_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index tell_FK on tell (
cno ASC
)
go

alter table tell
add constraint FK_TELL_TELL_COLLECTO foreign key (cno)
references collector (cno)
go

alter table tell
add constraint FK_TELL_TELL2_PATIENT foreign key (pno)
references patient (pno)
go
